00:02:58.196 --> 00:03:01.156 A:middle
Now local notifications
are the ones that are used

00:02:58.196 --> 00:03:01.156 A:middle
Now local notifications
are the ones that are used

00:03:01.156 --> 00:03:03.066 A:middle
by applications that
are on the device.

