the ones that are displayed

00:04:48.576 --> 00:04:49.746 A:middle
to the user on the device.

00:04:50.376 --> 00:04:53.216 A:middle
And by setting up your
notification payload the right

00:04:53.216 --> 00:04:56.346 A:middle
way, you can add this content
to be shown to the user.

00:04:57.626 --> 00:04:59.466 A:middle
As opposed to user-facing
notifications,

00:04:59.856 --> 00:05:02.126 A:middle
we also offer silent
update notifications.

00:04:59.856 --> 00:05:02.126 A:middle
we also offer silent
update notifications.

00:05:04.156 --> 00:05:06.786 A:middle
Now, these silent
update notifications work

00:05:07.126 --> 00:05:10.236 A:middle
where your notification payload
includes the content available

00:05:10.236 --> 00:05:13.786 A:middle
flag when this notification
